# Uptime Kuma — service monitoring dashboard
#
# Uptime Kuma monitors the availability of your services and sends alerts
# when something goes down. Uses SQLite (no external database needed).
#
# After first start, visit https://UK_HOSTNAME to create your admin account.
# Then add monitors for each service you want to track.

# UK_HOSTNAME: The public hostname Traefik routes to Uptime Kuma.
# Must match the entry in your Cloudflare tunnel config.yml ingress rules.
# Example: status.yourdomain.com
UK_HOSTNAME=status.yourdomain.com
